{
  "schemaVersion": 1,
  "id": "寻狗_庄家来人",
  "entry": "root",
  "meta": {
    "title": "寻狗Demo·入场钩子（面生雇主夜里寻背尸的：崖墓头七移尸）"
  },
  "nodes": {
    "root": {
      "type": "switch",
      "cases": [
        {
          "conditions": [
            {
              "plane": "背尸"
            }
          ],
          "next": "beishi_busy"
        },
        {
          "conditions": [
            {
              "narrative": "scenario_背尸",
              "state": "fled",
              "reached": true
            }
          ],
          "next": "done_1"
        }
      ],
      "defaultNext": "n1"
    },
    "done_1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "……那桩夜活，烂在肚子头。哪个问都没得。",
      "next": "end1",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "n1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "关二狗正骂骂咧咧拍身上的灰，一个面皮紧绷、面生得很的汉子直直走过来，上下打量他。",
      "next": "n2"
    },
    "n2": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "你就是那个背尸的？有桩背尸的活，今天黑了动身。",
      "next": "n3",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "n3": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "（压低声）城外临江崖墓，里头停的一具，要背下来送义庄。你只管背，别的莫问。",
      "next": "n3b",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "n3b": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "player"
      },
      "text": "崖墓里背下来？……人头七还没过吧？这就往外挪，不唱魂、不怕回煞撞起？",
      "next": "n3c",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "fear"
      }
    },
    "n3c": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "（脸一沉）莫多嘴。背到义庄就是，钱多给你。",
      "next": "n4",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "angry"
      }
    },
    "n4": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "「头七没过」「崖墓背尸」几个字一出，街边躲雨的几个人不约而同退开两步。只有关二狗站起没动——他被「工钱」两个字勾住了脚。",
      "next": "n_choice"
    },
    "n_choice": {
      "type": "choice",
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "xianqi",
          "text": "「晦气！大晦气！……先给好多？」",
          "next": "c_xianqi"
        },
        {
          "id": "jiele",
          "text": "「活人的钱难挣，死人的钱好挣。带路撒。」",
          "next": "c_jiele"
        }
      ]
    },
    "c_xianqi": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "（从袖里摸出一小串钱）定钱十文。事办成再给四十。嘴上嫌晦气，手倒是伸得快。",
      "next": "n_accept",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "smirk"
      }
    },
    "c_jiele": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "（多看了他一眼）撇脱。定钱十文，事办成再给四十。走撒。",
      "next": "n_accept",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "n_accept": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "emitNarrativeSignal",
          "params": {
            "sourceType": "dialogue",
            "sourceId": "寻狗_庄家来人",
            "signal": "beishi_hired"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "n5"
    },
    "n5": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "嘴上嫌晦气，眼睛早瞟向了那根背尸的旧绳。他跟着来人，摸黑往城外崖墓去——",
      "next": "n_go"
    },
    "n_go": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "switchScene",
          "params": {
            "targetScene": "崖墓",
            "targetSpawnPoint": "entry"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "end1"
    },
    "end1": {
      "type": "end"
    },
    "beishi_busy": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "你肩上驮个死人子，来谈我庄上的事？先送了，再来。",
      "next": "end1",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    }
  }
}
